      "description": "Welcome to the Victoria’s Secret App: Your go-to destination for discovering new trends, exclusive offers, the latest shopping and styling content & so much more.  \n \nWe have it all—from everyday bras, chic lingerie, and going-out clothes to signature fragrances and perfumes, we’ve got you (and every occasion you’re dressing for) fully covered. We're proud to offer intimates, clothes, activewear, and swimwear in sizes XS-XXL, cups AA-I, and bands 30-46. And that’s just the beginning—here are some other great things we have going on: \n \nDISCOVER YOUR NEW FAVORITE BRA \nShop every bra style at your fingertips. From full coverage to strapless and our fan-favorite push-up bras, there's so much to love. Our size range includes XS-XXL, cups AA-O, and bands 28-46. \n \nFIND CLOTHES FOR EVERY  OCCASION \nWith a wide selection of year-round staples and seasonal essentials, the Victoria’s Secret app offers collections like pajamas, activewear, and swimsuits. \n\n \n\nSHOP ICONIC FRAGRANCES  \n\nOur signature perfume and beauty include body mist, eau de parfum, and more body care. Explore all scent families and treat yourself—or find a gift for someone special. \n \nSMOOTH CHECKOUT \nSave your payment method for streamlined transactions and instantly manage your credit card. Find your local store in the app and explore same day delivery and in-store pickup options. \n \nJUST-FOR-YOU CONTENT \nTake fun quizzes, snag special offers, and view behind-the-scenes campaign videos with our models. Plus, other app offers. \n \nMEMBERS-ONLY PERKS \nJoin VS & PINK Rewards to earn points with every purchase, which turn into perks like free shipping and top-tier deals. Plus, you’ll get access to the Community—a space to create, connect, and get inspired. \n \nLike what you see? There’s more to explore. Follow along on social at @victoriassecret. We can’t wait to connect with you.",
